ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would call this a crash course in real-world engineering. It was gratifying to see everything come together in the final project.
Crash course in mechatronics! Relevant! Engaging! Empowering! Tremendous amount of learning and head-banging. Not for the faint of heart.
Yeah i would recommend this class especially to those who have had little experience with embedded controllers.
Yes I would. I liked the span of materials covered.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course was a very good opportunity to shore up some gaps in my undergraduate education. As such, I feel like I can approach my research with more confidence.
My research involves mechatronic systems, so this course was very helpful.
I will surely use embedded systems in my future research.
